'''Google Chat'''是[[Google|Google]]开发的一款通信软件，允許一對一聊天和群組聊天。Google將其視為[[Google_環聊|Google 環聊]]的替代者<ref name="de Looper, Christian">{{Cite web|title=Google will begin shutting down the classic Hangouts app in October|url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/social-media/google-hangouts-shut-down-2020/|accessdate=September 5, 2019|author=de Looper, Christian|work=DigitalTrends.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804113856/https://www.digitaltrends.com/social-media/google-hangouts-shut-down-2020/|archivedate=2019-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/9/21215588/google-chat-hangouts-meet-g-suite-name-change-rebranding|title=Google is rebranding Hangouts Chat as just Google Chat|first=Nick|last=Statt|date=2020-04-09|website=The Verge|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212031140/https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/9/21215588/google-chat-hangouts-meet-g-suite-name-change-rebranding|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.techradar.com/news/google-hangouts-officially-rebrands-as-google-chat|title=Google Hangouts officially rebrands as Google Chat|first=Mike Moore 10|last=April 2020|website=TechRadar|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210073431/https://www.techradar.com/news/google-hangouts-officially-rebrands-as-google-chat|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://bgr.com/2020/04/10/google-hangouts-vs-zoom-google-meet-and-google-chat-apps-for-g-suite/|title=Google’s messaging apps just got more confusing: Meet and Chat|first=Chris|last=Smith|date=2020-04-10|publisher=|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104233509/https://bgr.com/2020/04/10/google-hangouts-vs-zoom-google-meet-and-google-chat-apps-for-g-suite/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該款軟件最初名為'''Hangouts Chat'''，2020年4月更名為Google Chat<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/9/21215588/google-chat-hangouts-meet-g-suite-name-change-rebranding|title=Google is rebranding Hangouts Chat as just Google Chat|first=Nick|author=Statt|date=April 9, 2020|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212031140/https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/9/21215588/google-chat-hangouts-meet-g-suite-name-change-rebranding|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Google Chat最初只适用于[[Google_Workspace|Google Workspace]]用戶。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Compare G Suite products - Chat|url=https://gsuite.google.com/compare-editions/?feature=chat|accessdate=2020-04-29|work=gsuite.google.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822220836/https://gsuite.google.com/compare-editions/?feature=chat|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年起，Google Chat向所有用戶開放<ref>{{Cite web|title=Google Chat明年将向所有人开放 取代G套件中的Hangouts|url=https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1041105.htm|accessdate=cnbeta|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023083916/https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1041105.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Google Chat有管理員功能，這表示建立聊天室者能幾乎掌控聊天室。用戶必須透過Google Workspace帳戶使用Google Chat，才能編輯或刪除Chat訊息。<ref>{{Cite web|title=修改或删除消息 - 计算机 - Google Chat帮助|url=https://support.google.com/chat/answer/7653281|access-date=2022-01-24|work=support.google.com|archive-date=2022-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220330071437/https://support.google.com/chat/answer/7653281|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Google計劃在2022年初棄用Google 環聊，並用Google Chat取代。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Google Chat 升級時程 - Google Workspace 管理員說明|url=https://support.google.com/a/answer/9197126?hl=zh-Hant|access-date=2022-01-24|work=support.google.com|archive-date=2022-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124112230/https://support.google.com/a/answer/9197126?hl=zh-Hant|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Google_Hangouts_Chat_icon_(2017-2020).png|thumb]]Google Chat的舊稱為Hangouts Chat。在與[[Google_Meet|Hangouts Meet]]一同更名之後，Hangouts品牌從 Google Workspace中移除。

2021年8月，Google開始自動登出iOS和Android上的[[Google_环聊|Google 环聊]]用戶，並通知他們切換到Google Chat。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Li|first=Abner|date=2021-08-06|title=Google signing free users out of Hangouts for iOS, Android as part of 'switch to Chat' prompt|url=https://9to5google.com/2021/08/06/hangouts-signing-out-google-chat/|access-date=2022-01-24|website=9to5Google|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119223157/https://9to5google.com/2021/08/06/hangouts-signing-out-google-chat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
